  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\">\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <div style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\">\n      <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\">Produ</span><span leaf=\"\">ct Hunt是全球最流行的发掘有意思新产品的平台。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\">经过近十年的发展，已经成为用户发现新产品、创业者获得灵感、投资人寻找新机会，以及创始人对产品进行推广的最好地方。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">本期的月榜中，排名第四的华人产品 Macaron 是一款完全了解你的 AI 助理，排名第七的 nFactorial AI 则能让一众大佬免费为你讲课；此外，还有大量 AI 工具，涵盖工作流自动化、APP 构建、求职等方方面面。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">话不多说，下面就请来具体看看本期有趣的产品。</span></p>\n       <div style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\">\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">1.Trace：AI 工作流自动化工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">企业日常有许多重复性工作，如更新追踪、文档填写和团队协调，这些任务耗费了大量时间和精力，降低了员工的专注度。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Trace 是一款工作流自动化平台，用 AI 将任务拆解，并分配给人工或 AI Agent。其特点是集成 Slack、Jira 和 Notion 等工具，分解工作流的同时还可识别自动化机会，并将重复性任务嵌入 AI Agent，并可通过实时触发器和计划自动运行工作流。</span></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020640\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5978260869565217\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"736\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=edff9564&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCAzO9AdP8ahdN0tSerlPlUes051ZtwIicvqd5JfkHn8bHdFdgOPgibAXog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n        </figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Trace 提供免费版本；付费版定价为 60-200 美元/月，包含更多的积分、集成，以及其他高级功能。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1171</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：trace.so</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">2.Indy AI by Contra：AI 求职工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">求职者在寻找工作时，常在传统招聘平台耗费大量时间却效果不佳，同时可能错过自身社交网络中已存在的潜在优质机会。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Indy AI 的核心功能是作为个人助理，自动连接用户的 LinkedIn 和 X，扫描其扩展网络，并发现相关机会。用户只需设定偏好，Indy AI 便能智能读取 LinkedIn 和 X 上的帖子，推送匹配的机遇，还可根据用户点赞或不喜欢等反馈持续学习和优化推荐，自动化发现网络内最佳机会。</span></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020637\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"735\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35875121&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCAuQjlXlURlpXWOsrxuf5A8Pxx9Ol0DRycCEN3OYbMQIh8zFBCrYC6Hw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n        </figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Indy AI 提供免费版本。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1056</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：contra.com</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">3.Recall：个人 AI 笔记工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在日常学习和工作中，大家常遇到信息过载、记忆力有限以及难以高效整理和检索等问题。传统知识管理方式效率低下，导致重要信息易丢失，难以深入理解和发现知识间的联系。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Recall 主要针对个人知识管理和深度学习场景，旨在帮助用户“超越大脑记忆限制”。其核心功能是允许用户与所有阅读、观看、收听或记录的内容进行对话，并可随时添加或批量导入海量内容，构建一个自组织知识库。它能根据用户定义的来源提供个性化聊天体验，实现知识的即时检索与溯源，帮助用户发现信息间的深层联系，从而更深入地思考和理解。</span></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020641\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"704\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd62599e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCANicEwicS90KeM5ZteibShDMKibXPP2r9SCKYhlQ2KNYHEsQ6XN1zjFUiaiaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n        </figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Recall 提供免费版本；付费版定价为 10 美元/月起，包含无限内容总结与聊天、全知识库对话、自动分类、自动知识图谱等高级功能。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：899</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：getrecall.ai</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">4.Macaron AI：个人 AI 助理</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">第四名的这款充满人文关怀的产品来自我们华人团队！</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前许多 AI 应用侧重于提高生产力，却未能真正理解并记住用户的个人偏好、经验与需求，导致在日常生活中缺乏个性化和情感连接。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Macaron AI 主要针对个人日常生活的多种场景，旨在成为用户的专属 AI 助理。其核心功能在于通过强化学习，深入记忆用户的偏好、经验与愿望，并能即时生成个性化的“迷你应用”。这些迷你应用涵盖健身追踪、旅行规划、阅读伴侣、迷你游戏等，极大地丰富了 AI 在个人生活中的实用性，且用户可与朋友分享这些定制应用。</span></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020638\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6576980568011959\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"669\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=28b6ae25&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCAkqG6Lfd49h9Ym6HHBQ9P7ebIZPvftDLA2BYAd1d9NKs5C2ib0JQWdIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n        </figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Macaron AI 提供免费版本。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：857</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：macaron.im</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">5.Anything：AI APP 生成工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统软件产品开发通常需要用户具备专业的编程知识和技能，或者依赖多个独立的工具来完成设计、编码、数据库、支付和身份验证等复杂任务。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anything 主要面向希望快速构建移动或网页应用程序的个人和团队。其核心功能在于利用 AI Agent ，将用户描述转化为可运行的代码，并自动处理错误修复和项目重构等复杂任务。该产品的一个突出特色是它能够生成非 AI 风格的原创设计，并集成了数据库、身份验证、支付和多种 API 接口，确保用户可以构建出美观且功能完备的生产级应用。</span></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020639\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"735\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e4f2a5e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCAxHnQfKwkjSSuu9ya91GG6Ric8icnFEIl7g3DGOmPOwleJbBbTp6QmQfw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n        </figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-he