quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一位 AI 老师，都依托于他们的公开讲座生成，用 AI 模拟了他们的思维方式。如果你想与你的这些偶像们面对面交流，不妨一试。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020634\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6b653bd0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCAc0yHJSRtfPryl8rsiae3eIibUvLlTFvCUG8CflHWY7VtuI9bgr4MQMlg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">nFactorial AI 目前完全免费。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：714</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：nfactorialai.com</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">9.Mocke：AI 邮件处理工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前，Cold Email 营销面临测试周期长、缺乏有效反馈以及过度测试可能损害客户关系等痛点。营销人员难以快速验证邮件内容的市场契合度，导致效率低下且资源浪费。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Mocke 旨在解决 Cold Email 营销的测试难题，其核心功能是作为 AI Agent 模拟真实邮件营销活动，一分钟内即可提供预测的打开率、回复率和取消订阅率。Mocke 还支持揭示潜在客户的隐藏行为，如垃圾邮件举报、内部转发或忽略，从而深入分析营销活动的成败原因。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020635\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67a62fb3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCAoDuSaVgvKEmzMTnwsb7JeVB1HWpPPviadpd02n26CnOiaTCsicfhq4ybg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">Mocke 提供免费版本；付费版定价为 49 美元/月起，包含更多模拟额度、无限活动、Slack 支持等高级功能。</span>\n        </figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：674</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：mocke.co</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">10.X-Design：AI 图片处理工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">小型商家很难制作出温馨、逼真且专业的商品照片，他们往往缺乏专业的摄影棚或设计经验，导致产品图片难以在众多商品中脱颖而出。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">X-Design 旨在帮助小型商家轻松创建高质量产品图片，其核心功能是将单一产品照片转换为多种风格，如温馨卧室、波西米亚风客厅，并可生成主产品图、生活方式背景图、人物互动场景图及白底图等各个类型。X-Design 还支持一键式背景移除、尺寸调整、修饰和增强工具，以及自然的灯光、阴影和道具效果，让图片更具真实感。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020636\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5f72a67&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xmicL8zEicdejTa9x5NNuLsFCATCxHKhP2pUa6RAnQC0VAYZPeErhVWXjdJutRpiaJwYkU7IGGXhngpnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">X-Design 提供免费版本；付费版定价为 9.99 美元/月，包含移除物体或人物、AI 增强工具、专业级 AI 背景等高级功能。</span>\n        </figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：663</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：x-design.com</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
